<h1>Hazelwood Forest Apartment Homes</h1>
<h4>2 Bed / 2 Bath - 960 SQFT<br><br>Bed: 2<br>Bath: 2<br>Rent: 875<br>SQFT: 960<br><br></h4><h2>240 Chapel Ridge Drive<br>Hazelwood MO 63042</h2><h2> <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/stl/apa/7516420761/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
</h2>
Welcome home to Hazelwood Forest Apartments. Our one- and two-bedroom apartments homes feature large kitchens, dining areas, and spacious living rooms.
Come and enjoy your new home today! Hazelwood Forest Apartments is located in Hazelwood, Missouri in the 63042 zip code. Hazelwood’s residential neighborhoods are truly picturesque, featuring stately homes and charming apartment buildings with manicured landscaping. Stop by our clubhouse today and take a tour of our gorgeous community! Our community boasts a clubroom, oversized pool on park-like grounds. Call today to schedule your tour!<br><br>Hazelwood is a vibrant Saint Louis suburb situated just south of the Missouri River and just north of Saint Louis Lambert International Airport.  Hazelwood is dynamic, containing bustling commercial centers and tranquil residential neighborhoods. Commuting and traveling from Hazelwood is a breeze with convenience to I-170, I-270, and Saint Louis Lambert International Airport. Seventeen parks spanning over 179 acres contribute ample space for outdoor recreation in town. You can enjoy a park like setting right from your own patio or balcony! Take a dip in our oversized pool or a walk around the gorgeous community grounds. <br><br>More than 1,000 businesses are located in Hazelwood, including 12 Fortune 500 companies and 10 corporate headquarters. Consequently, many Hazelwood residents enjoy short commute times and abundant shopping opportunities at the Saint Louis Outlet Mall.<br><br> Located just minutes from Boeing and Lambert St. Louis International Airport.<h4>Apply on-line at www.damllc.info</h4><br><br><h4>Please inquire about our newly renovated apartment homes!</h4><h3>Our Amenities</h3><ul><li>Pets Welcome</li><li>Dishwasher Included</li><li>Custom Vertical &amp; Mini-Blinds</li><li>Maintenance &amp; Property Manager on Site</li><li>Assigned Parking</li><li>Laundry Facilities</li><li>Package Service</li><li>Walk-In Closets</li><li>Washer/Dryer Hookup in-unit</li><li>Sundeck or Balcony</li><li>Beautiful Clubhouse w/ Fireplace, Billiards Room &amp; Conversation Area</li><li>High Speed Internet Access</li></ul><br><br>
